# CODEOWNERS — per-satellite template.
#
# Each satellite installs this file at .github/CODEOWNERS. The substrate
# repo has its own CODEOWNERS at the equivalent path.
#
# v2 brief requirement: Christian on *, with a SEPARATE narrower scope
# for .github/workflows/** so workflow-file edits get extra attention.
# Branch protection's "Require review from Code Owners" reads this file.

# Default owner — everything not matched below.
* @cdonovan-abtex

# Workflow files — extra-careful zone. Same owner today, but listed
# separately so a future split (e.g. a "release engineer" role) is a
# one-line change here, not a CODEOWNERS rewrite.
/.github/workflows/ @cdonovan-abtex

# Substrate consumption — anything that pins the substrate version.
/pyproject.toml @cdonovan-abtex
/uv.lock @cdonovan-abtex

# Deploy + auth — agent-blocked paths (mirrors path_guard.py).
/deploy/ @cdonovan-abtex
/auth/ @cdonovan-abtex
/Dockerfile @cdonovan-abtex
